nodes.text: The Worker's District was a district of the city of Canto Bight, located on the planet Cantonica. The Sixth Kin criminal organization, led by Wen Delphis, was based out of the Worker's District during the Imperial Era. After his employment with the Tagge family was terminated, the assassin Just Lucky visited the Worker's District in order to meet Delphis and take a job for the Sixth Kin to pay off the debt of his brother, Pak, having done so previously.
